BobUI 4.6.1 is a bug-fix release. It maintains both forward and backward
compatibility (source and binary) with BobUI 4.6.0.  For more details,
refer to the online documentation included in this distribution. The
documentation is also available online:

  http://bobui.nokia.com/doc/4.6

The BobUI version 4.6 series is binary compatible with the 4.5.x series.
Applications compiled for 4.5 will continue to run with 4.6.

Some of the changes listed in this file include issue tracking numbers
corresponding to tasks in the BobUI Bug Tracker, the (now obsolete) Task
Tracker, or the Merge Request queue of the public source repository.

BobUI Bug Tracker: http://bugreports.bobui.nokia.com
Task Tracker:   http://bobui.nokia.com/developer/task-tracker
Merge Request:  http://bobui.gitorious.org

****************************************************************************
*                           General                                        *
****************************************************************************

Optimizations
-------------

 - Optimized empty QUrl creation
    * [BOBUIBUG-4030] Empty QUrls no longer allocate memory now

 * See list of Important Behavior Changes below


****************************************************************************
*                          Library                                         *
****************************************************************************

BobUICore
------

 - QFile
    * Improve performance of getting the canonical filename on Linux
      and Symbian by using realpath() system call.
    * Avoid stat() when opening a file.

 - QLibrary and QPluginLoader
    * Do not look at the BobUI patch-level version embedded in plugins'
      buildkeys when trying to determine if the plugin is compatible

 - QProcessEnvironment
    * [BOBUIBUG-6701] Ensure we don't crash in operator==

 - BOBUIextEncoder
    * [merge request 399] BOBUIextEncoder::fromUnicode as BOBUI3 support
      member

 - QXmlStreamreader
    * [merge request 1926] Fix parsing of DTDs that contain empty markup
      declarations.

BobUIGui
-----

 - QApplication
    * [BOBUIBUG-6654] Fix crashes when deleting QWidgets in touch event
      handlers.
 - QGraphicsEffect
    * [BOBUIBUG-5918] Fixed redraw bugs when using graphics effects on
      items while animating them by transformations.
 - QGraphicsItem
    * [BOBUIBUG-5917] Fixed memory leaks when removing a QGraphicsEffect from
      a QGraphicsItem or QWidget with setGraphicsEffect(0).
    * [BOBUIBUG-5859] Fixes incorrect rounding of the exposed rectangle of the
      QGraphicsItem causing painting issues when scaling the QGraphicsView.
    * [BOBUIBUG-5071] Fixes transformation problems when grouping/ungrouping
      the item with a QGraphicsItemGroup.
 - QGraphicsObject
    * 'id' property was removed. Use the 'objectName' property instead.
 - QGraphicsScene
    * [BOBUIBUG-6654] Fix crashes when deleting QGraphicsItems in touch
      event handlers.
 - QGraphicsView
    * [BOBUIBUG-6935] When using CacheBackground, the background is now
      correctly repainted after the QGraphicsView is shown after being
      hidden.
    * [BOBUIBUG-6835] Mouse tracking is now automatically enabled when using
      AnchorUnderMouse for view transformation.
    * [BOBUIBUG-6958] Fix speed regression in _q_polishItems()
    * [BOBUIBUG-6544] Fix a crash on the focus chain when removing items from 
      the scene.
    * Fix a crash in KDE/Plasma with QGraphicsView with topLevels.
 - QGraphicsWidget
    * [BOBUIBUG-6272] Only call updateFont if the font has changed.
 - QPainter
    * [BOBUIBUG-5939] Fixed incorrect redirection matrix that was causing
      wrong transformation for QGraphicsProxyWidgets.
    * [BOBUIBUG-6684] Added optimizations of 32-bit blend functions
      for ARM platforms with NEON support.
 - QPixmap
    * load() and loadFromData() can now support compressed GL textures
      in the DDS, ETC1, PVRTC2, and PVRTC4 formats if the OpenGL graphics
      system is active and the appropriate extensions are present in the
      GL implementation.
    * [BOBUIBUG-6840] Fixed load() to not modify referenced copies.
    * [BOBUIBUG-5840] Fixed a crash in fromImage() when passing in a null image.
    * [BOBUIBUG-6116] Fixed memory leak where a global object was not destroyed
      at program exit.
 - QPixmapCache
    * Fixed a small leak when using the new QPixmapCache::Key based API.
 - QPrinter
    * [BOBUIBUG-3412] QGraphicsProxyWidgets are now rendered correctly when
      printing a QGraphicsScene to PDF format.
 - QRasterPixmapData
    * [BOBUIBUG-6985] Fixed metric() to return the correct height in mm.
 - BOBUIextDocument
    * [BOBUIBUG-5397] Fixed printing of BOBUIextDocuments not including custom
      text objects.
    * [BOBUIBUG-6051] Fixed an endless loop when printing a BOBUIextDocument.

BobUIDBus
------

 - QDBusConnection
    * [BOBUIBUG-5979] Fixed the signal-delivery mechanism to update
      correctly when the sender name changes/appears on the bus.
    * [BOBUIBUG-7041] Fixed marshalling of booleans in release mode.
    * [BOBUI-2307] Fixed calls with the QDBus::BlockWithGui mode.
 - QDBusInterface
    * Made it continue working even when the remote object
      introspection fails.
 - QDBusInterface and qdbuscpp2xml
    * [BOBUIBUG-5563] Fixed an issue with generating annotations in
      signals.
 - QDBusPendingReply and QDBusReply
    * [BOBUIBUG-6571] Fixed a crash that would happen if you tried to
      make a call with a disconnected QDBusConnection.

BobUIMultimedia
------------

 - QAudioOutput
   * [Merge request 418] Fixed compilation the example provided for
     QAudioOutput::start.

BobUINetwork
---------

 - QNetworkAccessManager
    * HTTP: Send our locale with the HTTP request.
    * HTTP: Start Accept-language and Authorization header with capital letter.
    * HTTP: Fix caching algorithm, matching RFC 2612 and the documentation.
    * HTTP [BOBUIBUG-7060]: Fix an issue with headers like "private, max-age=300".
    * file: Introduce special subclass for higher performance with file:// URLs.
 - BOBUIcpSocket
    * [BOBUIBUG-5799] Fix waitForConnected() on Windows.
 - QNetworkProxyFactory
    * Fixed systemProxyForQuery(), it could sometimes return invalid empty list
      on Windows.
 - QNetworkCookieJar
    * [BOBUIBUG-5815] Do not check paths when accepting cookies.
 - QHostInfo
    * Use five parallel threads for host lookup instead of one.

BobUIOpenGL
--------

 - QGL2PaintEngineEx
    * Performance: Don't mark brush as dirty if it hasn't changed.
    * Performance: Use 3x3 PMV matrices rather than 4x4.
    * Performance: Move the 0.5 offset we add for aliased rendering to
      updateMatrix().
    * Performance: Remove superfluous enable/disable vertex attrib arrays.
    * Performance: Track the glVertexAttribPointer and only update it if it's
      changed.
    * [BOBUIBUG-7094]  Introduce new "snapToPixelGrid" flag for drawText.
 - QGLContext
    * bindTexture(QString) now supports DDS, ETC1, PVRTC2, and PVRTC4
      compressed textures if the appropriate extensions are present
      in the GL implementation.
    * bindTexture(QImage): Reduce double-copying of textures when flipping.
    * [BOBUIBUG-6454] Better EGL extension checking to avoid prefix problems
      with EGL_foo matching EGL_foo_bar.
    * [BOBUIBUG-6217] Work around problems with glColor4ub() on Intel Q45/Q43
      Express by consistently using glColor4f() everywhere.
    * bindTexture(QImage): Fix GL_BGRA formats under OpenGL/ES by using
      the same value for both internal and external texture formats.
    * [BOBUIBUG-5041] Disable depth testing while in renderText().
 - QGLEngineSelector
    * [BOBUIBUG-5638] Detect GL2 based on fragment shaders, not programs.
      Fragment programs are a GL1 feature.
 - QGLFramebufferObject
    * [BOBUIBUG-6712] Update docs to better explain how QPainter changes
      the GL state when used on an FBO.
 - QGLGlyphCache
    * [BOBUIBUG-6936] Fix memory leak of QGLGlyphCoord objects.
 - QGLPaintDevice
    * [BOBUIBUG-6204] Rebind window surface FBO after native GL rendering.
 - QGLPixmapData
    * [BOBUIBUG-6902] Align GL_RGB data on a 4-byte line boundary.
 - QGLWidget
    * [BOBUIBUG-5002, BOBUIBUG-6931] Fixed QGLWidget::renderText().
    * Fixed WA_TranslucentBackground for QGLWidgets on X11/EGL.
    * Fix EGL surface leaks when re-parenting on X11/EGL.
 - BOBUIriangulatingStroker
    * [BOBUIBUG-6045] Crash in dashed line handling in the GL stroker.

BobUIOpenVG
--------

 - [BOBUI-2555] Automatically destroy VG pixmaps when the last window surface
   goes away to reduce memory consumption of backgrounded applications.
 - [BOBUIBUG-6639] Recover from out-of-memory when creating VGImage's.
 - [BOBUI-2554] Add a VGImage allocation pool to support reclaiming older
   images when the GPU runs out of memory.
 - [BOBUIBUG-7051] Reset the OpenVG scissor after a native painting call-out.
 - [BOBUIBUG-7015] Avoid deep copies of QImage in QImage::bits() calls.

BobUIWebKit
--------

 - Fixed user agent string on Symbian (webkit.org/b/31961).
 - QWebInspector: Don't disable when hiding (webkit.org/b/31851).
 - Fix JavaScript prompt behaviour for empty/null strings (webkit.org/b/30914).
 - Fixed lastIndexOf() on Symbian (webkit.org/b/31773).
 - Fixed crash with Flash on Windows with MinGW.
 - Fixed wrapping of QObjects with recurring identity (webkit.org/b/31681).
 - Fixed compilation with ICC.
 - Fixed assertion when dragging SVG images (webkit.org/b/32511).
 - Added the framecapture example to the default build (merge request 2235)
 - Fixed crash with ACID3 test on Symbian
 - Fixed security issue XSL stylesheets and security origins.

BobUISql
-----

 - [BOBUIBUG-5373] Fixed QSqlRelationalTableModel doesn't correctly work with
   relation in other database schema.
 - [BOBUIBUG-5298] (OCI) Fixed QSqlDatabase.tables() does not work with system
   tables.
 - [BOBUIBUG-6421] Fixed setForwardOnly() for both OCI and SQLite.
 - [BOBUIBUG-6618] (ODBC) Fixed segfault when error string is larger than 256
