 - [BOBUIBUG-4461] (OCI) Fixed problem with clobs being handled as binary.

BobUISvg
-----

 - QSvgRenderer
    * [BOBUIBUG-6867] Fixed regression in the parsing of paths with relative
      offsets.
    * [BOBUIBUG-6899] Fixed crash when parsing invalid coordinate list.
 - BobUIXmlPatterns
    * [BOBUIBUG-6771] Fixed static builds.

BobUI Plugins
----------

 - JPEG plugin
    * Remove obsolete parameter string handling.
    * [BOBUI-2023] Re-implement ScaledSize, ClipRect, ScaledClipRect with
      libjpeg features for greater performance.
 - PBM plugin
    * [BOBUIBUG-6937] Use Mono instead of MonoLSB when writing pbm files.
 - TIFF plugin
